http://heather.cs.ucdavis.edu/~matloff/UnixAndC/CLanguage/Debug.html


gdb [program]

(gdb)

r - run

l - list
	l linenum
	l sourcefile:linenum

b - breakpoint
c - continue

	b linenum
	b function

disable breakpointnum - cancel breakpoint


d - display

disp variable

printf "i = %d\n" i


n - Next

s - Step

bt - backtrace

set variable i = 1


call func()


define xy
> printf "i = %d" i
> end


kill


==== faq

list breakpoint
> info break

debug child process

> set follow-fork-mode child


